Configuring message logging for Modbus TCP or OPC UA connectivity follows the same procedure as configuring message logging for Edge System as a whole.
	
The schema files Modbus.Logging.Schema.json and OpcUa.Logging.Schema.json for configuring message logging for Edge Connectivity are located in:
•	Windows: %ProgramFiles%/OSIsoft/EdgeSystem/Schema
•	Linux: /opt/EdgeSystem/Schema
For more information, see Message logging configuration.
